commit.message:
Redesign calendar UX: explicit submit button, compact layout, inline date picker

- CalendarCellClassless: remove auto-save-on-blur; now opens modal on click
  with meal type selector, counters, memo, and single "変更を申請する" button
- CalendarCellClassless: compact aspect fills grid row, shows count summary
- OrderModal: rename button to "変更を申請する" with ring-4 ring-orange-100 highlight
- ClassReportPanel: integrate date picker for effective_from (scheduled changes);
  save now uses updateKindergartenClasses to trigger email notification;
  remove dependency on ClassChangeRequestModal
- page.tsx: compact unsubmitted state (inline card instead of full-page hero);
  grid uses auto-rows-[5rem] to fix cells being too tall on desktop;
  remove ClassChangeRequestModal and isChangeRequestOpen state;
  pass mealOptions to CalendarCellClassless

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
